</div><h2>Categories > Entertainment
</h2><p>IMG plays an important and growing role in entertainment.</p>

<p>We represent top talent, such as Justin Timberlake and Taylor Swift. Our broadcasting practice includes major anchors on top television networks in the U.S. And we're growing new entertainment crossover businesses in emerging markets, like India and Brazil. We also deliver a variety of arts and entertainment events, including the Tutankhamun Exhibition in Australia, Nobel Peace Prize concerts in Oslo and the British Military Tournament in London.</p>

<p>IMG produces and distributes entertainment programming worldwide. In conjunction with our media distribution arm, we market and distribute a catalogue of hundreds of hours of programming in virtually every major country in the world - across a wide range of genres, from Timewatch and Models Live to Seducing Cindy.</p>

<p>To learn more about opportunities across entertainment, choose a link below:</p>
